classDiagram
class Gateway
class Service
class Repo
class Cache
Gateway --> Service : receives<br>request
Service --> Gateway : returns<br>response
Service --> Repo : persists<br>state
Repo --> Service : hydrates<br>state
Service --> Cache : reads<br>fast path
Cache --> Service : invalidates<br>entry
Repo --> Cache : warms<br>cache
Cache --> Repo : evicts<br>stale
